The upper bound directly follows from Corollary~\ref{cor:upperboundonProf}, so we focus on the lower bound. 

We know from Corollary~\ref{cor:lowerboundonProf} that we must determine the asymptotic behaviour of $\varphi^{-1}$, where $\varphi(x)=x\cdot\Lambda_{\cloner{H}}(x)$. By definition, we have that $\varphi^{-1}(x)\cdot\Lambda_{\cloner{H}}(\varphi^{-1}(x))=x$, and thus 
\begin{equation*}
    \ln(\varphi^{-1}(x))+\ln(\Lambda_{\cloner{H}}(\varphi^{-1}(x)))=\ln(x).
