\end{equation*}
whence $\varphi^{-1}(x) \simeq \sqrt{\ln(x)}$. From Lemma~\ref{lem:UsefulLemmaProfile}, it follows that $\profp{H}(\varphi^{-1}(x))\simeq \profp{H}\left(\sqrt{\ln(x)}\right)$, and we are done.

